# &quot;Fast Food Song&quot; (Shanghai Surprise &#x27;Go Large&#x27; club mix) – 6:05
# &quot;Fast Food Song&quot; (Sing-A-Long-A-Fast-Food) – 3:08
# &quot;Fast Food Song&quot; (video)

