<doc id="280989" wikidata="Q4922290" url="?curid=280989" title="Black chanterelle">
<text>Black chanterelle is a common name of several fungi species and can refer to:

*&quot;Craterellus cornucopioides&quot;
*&quot;Craterellus cinereus&quot;
*&quot;Craterellus atrocinereus&quot;
*&quot;Polyozellus multiplex&quot;</text><links>
